<h1>Office Equipment Charlotte, NC</h1>

			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->
					
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_row --><div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_1">
				
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3  et_pb_column_1">
				
				<div class="et_pb_blurb et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_center  et_pb_blurb_0 et_pb_blurb_position_top">
				<div class="et_pb_blurb_content">
					<div class="et_pb_main_blurb_image"><img src="http://www.cbtsales.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/cbt-blurb.jpg" alt="Charlotte Office Equipment" class="et-waypoint et_pb_animation_off" /></div>
					<div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
						
						
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Carolina Business Technologies, the trusted source for office equipment sales &amp; leasing in the greater Charlotte area,  offers a variety of models for your office or business such as state-of-the-art digital copiers, <a href="http://www.cbtsales.com/products/laser-printers/">laser printers</a>, and supplies</strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">CBT features a trusted line of products from internationally known manufactures including Kyocera, Copystar and Oki.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.cbtsales.com/contact-us/">Carolina Business Technolog</a>y serves the Charlotte, Rock Hill, and surrounding areas. Our office equipment repair solutions and driven customer service caters to multi-user environments who expect consistent results.</p>

					</div>
				</div> <!-- .et_pb_blurb_content -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_blurb -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column --><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3  et_pb_column_2">
				
				<div class="et_pb_blurb et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_center  et_pb_blurb_1 et_pb_blurb_position_top">
				<div class="et_pb_blurb_content">
					<div class="et_pb_main_blurb_image"><img src="http://www.cbtsales.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/CBTCOPIERS.jpg" alt="Charlotte Office Equipment Rental" class="et-waypoint et_pb_animation_off" /></div>
					<div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
						
						
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>CBT Copier Rentals offers a wide variety of copiers on your terms to individuals and businesses in the greater Charlotte, NC area. </strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Our daily, weekly and monthly copier rental rates and our selection of copiers are sure to fit your needs and your budget.</p>
<ul>
<li style="text-align: left;">Models ranging from 20 to 80 copies per minute</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Console and desktop models available</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Print, scan and fax options are available on all models</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Largest copier rental inventory in Charlotte</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Next day delivery.</li>
</ul>

					</div>
				</div> <!-- .et_pb_blurb_content -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_blurb -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column --><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_3  et_pb_column_3">
				
				<div class="et_pb_blurb et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_center  et_pb_blurb_2 et_pb_blurb_position_top">
