					<div class="et_pb_main_blurb_image"><img src="http://www.cbtsales.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/fleet-blurb.jpg" alt="Charlotte Office Equipment Services" class="et-waypoint et_pb_animation_off" /></div>
					<div class="et_pb_blurb_container">
						
						
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>We are conveniently located in South Charlotte, able to quickly service the uptown area as well as the fast growing Upstate South Carolina business community.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">CBT can provide onsite service to the following cities around Charlotte: Pineville, Matthews, Mint Hill, Waxhaw, Monroe, Harrisburg, Belmont, Mt. Holly, Gastonia, Kings Mountain, Huntersville, Cornelius, Davidson and Concord.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">In South Carolina our service area includes;: Rock Hill, Fort Mill, Lake Wylie, Clover, York, Lancaster, Chester and Tega Cay.</p>

